1. OWNERSHIP
Alberto García-Lluis Valencia (the "Owner") is the sole intellectual owner of the
theoretical model, algorithms, source code, derived data, reports, figures,
dashboard and the entire development contained in this repository (the "Work").
All intellectual and industrial property rights in the Work are reserved to the
Owner.

2. USES PERMITTED WITHOUT PRIOR AUTHORIZATION
The following are permitted, free of charge and revocably, for NON-COMMERCIAL
purposes only:
   (a) viewing, reading and downloading the Work;
   (b) use for personal study, teaching and academic research;
   (c) citation with express attribution to the Owner, per CITATION.cff.
Any such use must preserve this license notice and the authorship attribution.

3. USES REQUIRING WRITTEN AUTHORIZATION
Any COMMERCIAL use of the Work or of the information it contains is PROHIBITED
without the prior written authorization of the Owner, including, without
limitation:
   (a) its exploitation, commercialization, sale, sublicensing or assignment;
   (b) its incorporation into for-profit products, services or processes;
   (c) the provision of consulting, advisory or analytical services based on the
       Work;
   (d) its use by for-profit entities, public or private, within their economic
       activity.
Authorization must be obtained from the Owner in writing and may be subject to
the financial and usage conditions the Owner determines.

4. INDEMNIFICATION FOR UNAUTHORIZED USE
Commercial use of the Work without the written authorization required in
clause 3 shall constitute a breach entitling the Owner to compensation equal to
FORTY PERCENT (40%) of the total revenue obtained by the infringer in connection
with such use up to the moment it ceases, as consequential damage and loss of
profit, without prejudice to any other legal action available to the Owner and
to the obligation to cease the use immediately.

5. NO WARRANTY
The Work is provided "AS IS", without warranty of any kind. The Owner shall not
be liable for any claim, damages or other liability arising from use of the Work.

6. GOVERNING LAW AND JURISDICTION
This license is governed by Spanish law. Any dispute shall be submitted to the
competent courts under the applicable law.

